description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Tennis finals - Newport, '13 1913 Aug. 27 (date created or published later by Bain) 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title and date from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negative. Photo shows the United States National Championship tennis finals at Newport Casino, Newport, Rhode Island. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2010) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication.
